CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 3, 1958, pg. 9 reads: "NAACP Youth Council Officers - The new officers of the Youth Council of the Pittsburgh chapter of the NAACP, who were elected Monday night at a meeting at the NAACP office downtown, are (seated) Miss Freda Blanton, secretary; Charles H. Shelton Jr., president. Standing: Wayne W. R. Holt, vice president, and Samuel T. Tyler, treasurer. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Youth Council of Pittsburgh chapter of NAACP officers, seated: Freda Blanton and Charles H. Shelton Jr.; standing: Wayne W. R. Holt and Samuel T. Tyler, gathered around table in NAACP office, Downtown
